@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title Context: L1 (Fizic) si L2 (Legatura de date)

rectangle "L3 Retea\n(IP)" as L3
rectangle "L2 Legatura de date\n(cadre, MAC, CRC)" as L2
rectangle "L1 Fizic\n(biti, semnal)" as L1
rectangle "Mediu\n(cablu / fibra / aer)" as MED

L3 -down-> L2
L2 -down-> L1
L1 -down-> MED

note right of L2
  L2 rezolva limitari L1:
  - adresare locala (MAC)
  - delimitare cadre
  - detectie erori (CRC)
end note
@enduml
